{"title":"刷题笔记&反思","uid":"9f834bd1d2ffa8c0cd255a8bbb4dc75a","slug":"P1059","date":"2025-10-28T11:58:09.000Z","updated":"2025-11-13T07:36:05.491Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/P1059.json","keywords":"Catice, 猫冰","cover":null,"content":"<h2 id=\"luogu-P1059\"><a href=\"#luogu-P1059\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"luogu P1059\"></a>luogu P1059</h2><p>类型：双指针 | 排序</p>\n<h4 id=\"题目描述\"><a href=\"#题目描述\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"题目描述\"></a>题目描述</h4><p>明明想在学校中请一些同学一起做一项问卷调查，为了实验的客观性，他先用计算机生成了 N 个 1 到 1000 之间的随机整数 (N≤100)，对于其中重复的数字，只保留一个，把其余相同的数去掉，不同的数对应着不同的学生的学号。然后再把这些数从小到大排序，按照排好的顺序去找同学做调查。请你协助明明完成“去重”与“排序”的工作。</p>\n<p>输入格式<br>输入有两行，第 1 行为 1 个正整数，表示所生成的随机数的个数 N。</p>\n<p>第 2 行有 N 个用空格隔开的正整数，为所产生的随机数。</p>\n<p>输出格式<br>输出也是两行，第 1 行为 1 个正整数 M，表示不相同的随机数的个数。</p>\n<p>第 2 行为 M 个用空格隔开的正整数，为从小到大排好序的不相同的随机数。</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br><span class=\"line\">21</span><br><span class=\"line\">22</span><br><span class=\"line\">23</span><br><span class=\"line\">24</span><br><span class=\"line\">25</span><br><span class=\"line\">26</span><br><span class=\"line\">27</span><br><span class=\"line\">28</span><br><span class=\"line\">29</span><br><span class=\"line\">30</span><br><span class=\"line\">31</span><br><span class=\"line\">32</span><br><span class=\"line\">33</span><br><span class=\"line\">34</span><br><span class=\"line\">35</span><br><span class=\"line\">36</span><br><span class=\"line\">37</span><br><span class=\"line\">38</span><br><span class=\"line\">39</span><br><span class=\"line\">40</span><br><span class=\"line\">41</span><br><span class=\"line\">42</span><br><span class=\"line\">43</span><br><span class=\"line\">44</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">#include &lt;iostream&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">using namespace std;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">const int N = 110;</span><br><span class=\"line\">int a[N];</span><br><span class=\"line\">int n;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">void quick_sort(int l, int r)</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    if (l &gt;= r) return;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    int x = a[l + r &gt;&gt; 1], i = l - 1, j = r + 1;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">    while (i &lt; j)</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        do i++; while(a[i] &lt; x);</span><br><span class=\"line\">        do j--; while(a[j] &gt; x);</span><br><span class=\"line\">        if (i &lt; j) swap(a[i], a[j]);</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    quick_sort(l, j), quick_sort(j + 1, r);</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">int main(void)</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    scanf(&quot;%d&quot;, &amp;n);</span><br><span class=\"line\">    for (int i = 0; i &lt; n; i++) scanf(&quot;%d&quot;, &amp;a[i]);</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">    quick_sort(0, n - 1);</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">    int count = 1;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    for (int p1 = 0, p2 = 1; p2 &lt; n; p2++)</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        if (a[p1] &lt; a[p2])</span><br><span class=\"line\">        &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            p1++;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            a[p1] = a[p2];</span><br><span class=\"line\">            count++;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">    cout &lt;&lt; count &lt;&lt; endl;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    for (int i = 0; i &lt; count; i++)</span><br><span class=\"line\">        cout &lt;&lt; a[i] &lt;&lt; &quot; &quot;;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<h4 id=\"总结\"><a href=\"#总结\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"总结\"></a>总结</h4><p><strong>我对for循环的理解</strong><br>for (1; 2; 3)</p>\n<p>对于2边界条件的思考</p>\n<ul>\n<li>代码块被执行时，判断条件都是满足的<ul>\n<li>如<code>for( ; i &lt; n; )</code>，在整个for循环代码块的执行过程中，i都是小于n的</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>最后变量的状态是，变量最后一次执行的状态 + 3中修改的状态<ul>\n<li>如<code>for ( ; i &lt; n; i++)</code>，最后i的状态是，i &#x3D; n - 1，最后再 ++1</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>双指针去重算法</strong><br>记住有这种线性的去重算法，前提是数组是有序的<br>核心概念就是<br><strong>把不重复的元素都放在数组前面去</strong><br>这一个操作需要两个定位点，也就是前指针和后指针，才能完成这个<strong>交换</strong>操作<br>类似的思想还有快速排序中的交换</p>\n<h2 id=\"ackwing-800-数组元素的目标和\"><a href=\"#ackwing-800-数组元素的目标和\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"ackwing 800 数组元素的目标和\"></a>ackwing 800 数组元素的目标和</h2><p>类型：双指针</p>\n<h4 id=\"题目描述-1\"><a href=\"#题目描述-1\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"题目描述\"></a>题目描述</h4><p>给定两个升序排序的有序数组 A 和 B ，以及一个目标值 x 。</p>\n<p>数组下标从 0 开始。</p>\n<p>请你求出满足 A[i]+B[j]&#x3D;x 的数对 (i,j) 。</p>\n<p>数据保证有唯一解。</p>\n<p>输入格式<br>第一行包含三个整数 n,m,x<br>，分别表示 A 的长度，B 的长度以及目标值 x</p>\n<p>第二行包含 n 个整数，表示数组 A</p>\n<p>第三行包含 m 个整数，表示数组 B</p>\n<p>输出格式<br>共一行，包含两个整数 i 和 j</p>\n<p>数据范围<br>数组长度不超过 10^5<br>同一数组内元素各不相同。<br>1≤数组元素≤10^9</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br><span class=\"line\">21</span><br><span class=\"line\">22</span><br><span class=\"line\">23</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">#include &lt;iostream&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">using namespace std;</span><br><span class=\"line\">const int N = 1e5 + 10;</span><br><span class=\"line\">int a[N], b[N];</span><br><span class=\"line\">int n, m, k;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">int main(void)</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    scanf(&quot;%d %d %d&quot;, &amp;n, &amp;m, &amp;k);</span><br><span class=\"line\">    for (int i = 0; i &lt; n; i++) scanf(&quot;%d&quot;, &amp;a[i]);</span><br><span class=\"line\">    for (int i = 0; i &lt; m; i++) scanf(&quot;%d&quot;, &amp;b[i]);</span><br><span class=\"line\">    </span><br><span class=\"line\">    int l = 0, r = m - 1;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    while (a[l] + b[r] != k) // 一定有可能解，所以不用框定范围</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        while (a[l] + b[r] &gt; k) r--;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        while (a[l] + b[r] &lt; k) l++;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    </span><br><span class=\"line\">    </span><br><span class=\"line\">    cout &lt;&lt; l &lt;&lt; &quot; &quot; &lt;&lt; r;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>不一定有可能解版本</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">for (int i = 0, j = m - 1; i &lt; n; i ++) &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    while(j &gt;= 0 &amp;&amp; a[i] + b[j] &gt; k) j --;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    if(j &gt;= 0 &amp;&amp; a[i] + b[j] == k) printf(&quot;%d %d\\n&quot;, i, j);</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<h4 id=\"总结-1\"><a href=\"#总结-1\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"总结\"></a>总结</h4><h2 id=\"luogu-P1314\"><a href=\"#luogu-P1314\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"luogu P1314\"></a>luogu P1314</h2><p>二分 + 前缀和 + 数学<br>普及+</p>\n<h4 id=\"题目描述-2\"><a href=\"#题目描述-2\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"题目描述\"></a>题目描述</h4><p>质检员检查矿石那道题</p>\n<h4 id=\"题解\"><a href=\"#题解\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"题解\"></a>题解</h4><p>我自己做出来了！！</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br><span class=\"line\">21</span><br><span class=\"line\">22</span><br><span class=\"line\">23</span><br><span class=\"line\">24</span><br><span class=\"line\">25</span><br><span class=\"line\">26</span><br><span class=\"line\">27</span><br><span class=\"line\">28</span><br><span class=\"line\">29</span><br><span class=\"line\">30</span><br><span class=\"line\">31</span><br><span class=\"line\">32</span><br><span class=\"line\">33</span><br><span class=\"line\">34</span><br><span class=\"line\">35</span><br><span class=\"line\">36</span><br><span class=\"line\">37</span><br><span class=\"line\">38</span><br><span class=\"line\">39</span><br><span class=\"line\">40</span><br><span class=\"line\">41</span><br><span class=\"line\">42</span><br><span class=\"line\">43</span><br><span class=\"line\">44</span><br><span class=\"line\">45</span><br><span class=\"line\">46</span><br><span class=\"line\">47</span><br><span class=\"line\">48</span><br><span class=\"line\">49</span><br><span class=\"line\">50</span><br><span class=\"line\">51</span><br><span class=\"line\">52</span><br><span class=\"line\">53</span><br><span class=\"line\">54</span><br><span class=\"line\">55</span><br><span class=\"line\">56</span><br><span class=\"line\">57</span><br><span class=\"line\">58</span><br><span class=\"line\">59</span><br><span class=\"line\">60</span><br><span class=\"line\">61</span><br><span class=\"line\">62</span><br><span class=\"line\">63</span><br><span class=\"line\">64</span><br><span class=\"line\">65</span><br><span class=\"line\">66</span><br><span class=\"line\">67</span><br><span class=\"line\">68</span><br><span class=\"line\">69</span><br><span class=\"line\">70</span><br><span class=\"line\">71</span><br><span class=\"line\">72</span><br><span class=\"line\">73</span><br><span class=\"line\">74</span><br><span class=\"line\">75</span><br><span class=\"line\">76</span><br><span class=\"line\">77</span><br><span class=\"line\">78</span><br><span class=\"line\">79</span><br><span class=\"line\">80</span><br><span class=\"line\">81</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">#include &lt;iostream&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">#include &lt;vector&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">#include &lt;algorithm&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">#include &lt;cmath&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">using namespace std;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">const int N = 200010;</span><br><span class=\"line\">const int W = 1e6 + 10; // 二分，如果不知道具体范围，就选一个合适的大整数来初始化</span><br><span class=\"line\">int n, m;</span><br><span class=\"line\">long long s, res = 1e13; // 同时结果的初始化也是</span><br><span class=\"line\">int w;</span><br><span class=\"line\">// 对于mines，第一个为重量，第二个为价值</span><br><span class=\"line\">vector&lt;pair&lt;int, int&gt;&gt; mines, queries; // 注意：矿石从1开始编号</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">int a[N];</span><br><span class=\"line\">int s1[N], s2[N]; // 第一个为布尔值的和，第二个为价值与布尔值的和</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">long long check(int w)</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    long long res = 0;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    </span><br><span class=\"line\">    for (int i = 0; i &lt; n; i++) // 构建布尔值原列表，从1开始</span><br><span class=\"line\">        a[i + 1] = (mines[i].first &gt;= w);</span><br><span class=\"line\">    </span><br><span class=\"line\">    for (int i = 1; i &lt;= n; i++) // 构建前缀和列表</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        s1[i] = s1[i - 1] + a[i];</span><br><span class=\"line\">        s2[i] = s2[i - 1] + a[i] * mines[i - 1].second;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">    for (auto item : queries) // 变量询问</span><br><span class=\"line\">        res += (s1[item.second] - s1[item.first - 1]) * (s2[item.second] - s2[item.first - 1]); // 计算检验值的和</span><br><span class=\"line\">    return res;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">int main(void)</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    scanf(&quot;%d %d %lld&quot;, &amp;n, &amp;m, &amp;s);</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">    for (int i = 0; i &lt; n; i++)</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        int w, v;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        scanf(&quot;%d %d&quot;, &amp;w, &amp;v);</span><br><span class=\"line\">        mines.push_back(&#123;w, v&#125;);</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">    for (int i = 0; i &lt; m; i++)</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        int l, r;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        scanf(&quot;%d %d&quot;, &amp;l, &amp;r);</span><br><span class=\"line\">        queries.push_back(&#123;l, r&#125;);</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">    int mid, l = 0, r = W;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    long long y; // w越大，y越小</span><br><span class=\"line\">    while (l &lt; r)</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        mid = l + r &gt;&gt; 1;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        y = check(mid);</span><br><span class=\"line\">        res = min(res, abs(y - s));</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">        if (s &gt;= y) r = mid; // 标准值小了，说明要把</span><br><span class=\"line\">        else l = mid + 1;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">    cout &lt;&lt; res;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">/**</span><br><span class=\"line\"> * 二分查找的题实际上都可以用二分答案做，二分答案能保证有结果</span><br><span class=\"line\"> * 只不过最后需要手动判断一下，结果是否符合条件</span><br><span class=\"line\"> * </span><br><span class=\"line\"> * 很不错，挑战了一个高于自己水平的题，竟然还有思路</span><br><span class=\"line\"> * 但最终败在不同类型的值的区分上</span><br><span class=\"line\"> * y我最先给的int，所以爆了，于是我一直纠结是不是我二分逻辑的问题</span><br><span class=\"line\"> * 下次注意检查的时候先检查类型是否匹配，因为这个比算法逻辑好检查一些</span><br><span class=\"line\"> *</span><br><span class=\"line\"> * 同时我也学会了题目给的数据圈定范围的能力</span><br><span class=\"line\"> * 而且理解了无限大和无限小在初始化值时候的好处</span><br><span class=\"line\">*/</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>","text":"luogu P1059类型：双指针 | 排序 题目描述明明想在学校中请一些同学一起做一项问卷调查，为了实验的客观性，他先用计算机生成了 N 个 1 到 1000...","permalink":"/post/P1059","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"4.6k","symbolsTime":"4 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"algorithm","slug":"algorithm","count":2,"path":"api/categories/algorithm.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"notes","slug":"notes","count":1,"path":"api/tags/notes.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#luogu-P1059\"><span class=\"toc-text\">luogu P1059</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-4\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E9%A2%98%E7%9B%AE%E6%8F%8F%E8%BF%B0\"><span class=\"toc-text\">题目描述</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-4\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E6%80%BB%E7%BB%93\"><span class=\"toc-text\">总结</span></a></li></ol></li></ol></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#ackwing-800-%E6%95%B0%E7%BB%84%E5%85%83%E7%B4%A0%E7%9A%84%E7%9B%AE%E6%A0%87%E5%92%8C\"><span class=\"toc-text\">ackwing 800 数组元素的目标和</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-4\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E9%A2%98%E7%9B%AE%E6%8F%8F%E8%BF%B0-1\"><span class=\"toc-text\">题目描述</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-4\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E6%80%BB%E7%BB%93-1\"><span class=\"toc-text\">总结</span></a></li></ol></li></ol></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#luogu-P1314\"><span class=\"toc-text\">luogu P1314</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-4\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E9%A2%98%E7%9B%